    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054110/extras/9b3b5b941bc04f02104c3cfe276ea411.avif?t=1765430836\" width=600 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finding yourself lost on an unfamiliar road, you decide to ask for directions at a nearby estate. You should have known that the splendor of this place was not meant for the likes of you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soon enough, you'll understand the consequences for this vulgar intrusion.      <br><br><strong>Beaux-Arts</strong> is a surreal, narrative-focused horror game about cruelty, suffering, and beauty.      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054110/extras/d1e71043d3cc5ba15bdf145bea36888a.poster.avif?t=1765430836\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054110/extras/d1e71043d3cc5ba15bdf145bea36888a.webm?t=1765430836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054110/extras/d1e71043d3cc5ba15bdf145bea36888a.mp4?t=1765430836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054110/extras/cb2910cb0402475d73e826fc6c87434a.avif?t=1765430836\" width=600 height=67 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wander the estate, examine its refined features, and learn about its noble history.  You'll have time to contemplate and discuss the magnificence of your surroundings, if you so wish.   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SPEAK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to the family and staff of the estate. Not everyone here wants to hurt you, and perhaps they can even help you leave this place. Then again, they might also have their own reasons to be reticent in offering aid... </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WAIT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt to the rhythms, movements and lulls of life in the manor. The residents will move about the grounds as they please, but do not assume that you can do the same. As prisoner of the household, freedom of movement is a privilege that must be earned and can be revoked.</p>",
